    <name>MangoManager</name>
    <summary>A simple GUI to manage MangoHud profiles</summary>
    <developer id="io.github.Marxis95">
        <name>Marxis95</name>
    </developer>

    <description>
        <p>
            MangoHud Profile Manager is a lightweight graphical tool designed to make MangoHud configuration easy.
            Instead of editing text files, you can manage your performance overlay profiles through
            a clean and intuitive interface.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Create and switch between multiple MangoHud profiles.</li>
            <li>Real-time process monitoring using psutil.</li>
            <li>Easy desktop integration.</li>
        </ul>
    </description>

